llip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/27/24229994/boox-go-6-palma-cheaper-e-reader" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/27/24229994/boox-go-6-palma-cheaper-e-reader</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-27T16:49:38-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-27T16:49:38-04:00</updated><title>在 Apple 下一次硬件活动之前，Apple Watch Ultra 2 降价 100 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉红色反光表面上的 Apple Watch Ultra 2&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/VuEvm2BpDB1MGMOYe7egFZ9NjZw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73547712/236790_Apple_watch_9_Ultra_2_AKrales_0978.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;传闻甚多的 Apple Watch Ultra 3 可能配备更快的处理器，但当前型号也毫不逊色。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Tx8gc1&quot;>;苹果的下一次硬件活动正式举行&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/26 /24223957/apple-iphone-16-launch-event-date-glowtime&quot;>;定于 9 月 9 日&lt;/a>; 东部时间下午 1 点/太平洋时间上午 10 点。人们普遍认为，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/17/24222355/iphone-16-rumors-leaks-cameras&quot;>;即将推出的 iPhone 16&lt;/a>; 将成为该节目，尽管&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/23/24227030/apple-iphone-16-watch-series-10-airpods-launch-event-date-rumor&quot; >;传言&lt;/a>;是可信的，苹果还可能利用此次展示推出新款 Apple Watch Series 10 和 Watch Ultra 3。也就是说，苹果第三代智能手表的首发价格不太可能低于 799 美元，这使得我们在 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CSTHHVBM/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a 看到 100 美元折扣>; 在 &lt;strong>;Apple Watch Ultra 2 &lt;/strong>;上更甜蜜。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;CNVbkH&quot;>;&lt;div data -anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何选择购买哪款 Apple Watch&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www. theverge.com/23037